</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Moody Blues will be inducted into Hollywood's Rock Walk on Tuesday, 
leaving their handprints and signatures on a cement block of sidewalk on Sunset 
Boulevard. 
</P>
<P>
