THE PEOPLE'S HOUSE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 President Clinton calls the White House "the people's house." Going further, 
we could call the Capitol building "the lobbyists' house." 
</P>
<P>
 ROBERT L. McREYNOLDS 
</P>
