<P>
 LOSS LEAVES THEM SORT OF AT A LOSS 
</P>
<P>
 After being thoroughly dominated by the Huskies in the second half, some of 
the Hurricanes described their feelings after the game. 
</P>
<P>
 "I'm really sort of sick," Miami Coach Dennis Erickson said. "I've never been 
around a game like that, what happened in the second half. 
</P>
<P>
