<DOCID> 082715 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 25, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Magazine; Page 12; Magazine Desk 
</P>
